      <main class="container">
        <section class="card">
          <h2>What is the OUIAA Scholarship?</h2>
          <p>
            The OUIAA Scholarship is a prestigious, merit-based initiative
            designed to support undergraduate students at Oduduwa University who
            show:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Academic excellence</li>
            <li>Resilience in the face of hardship</li>
            <li>Leadership potential</li>
            <li>A desire to impact their community positively</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            It is funded by alumni and sponsors who believe in empowering young
            minds. Awards may cover partial or full tuition for the academic year.
          </p>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Full-time undergraduate at Oduduwa University</li>
            <li>Currently in 200 level or higher</li>
            <li>Minimum CGPA of 3.5 on a 5.0 scale</li>
            <li>Provide a personal and financial impact statement</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Key Application Components</h2>
          <div class="grid">
            <div><strong>Academic Performance</strong></div>
            <div><strong>Impact Statement</strong></div>
            <div><strong>Leadership & Community</strong></div>
            <div><strong>Presentation</strong></div>
          </div>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Academic Performance</h2>
          <p>
            Minimum CGPA: 3.5 (4.0+ preferred). Include your official transcript
            to support your application.
          </p>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Personal & Financial Impact Statement</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Background and financial status</li>
            <li>Challenges you’ve overcome</li>
            <li>Motivation for your course</li>
            <li>Academic and career goals</li>
            <li>How the scholarship would impact your life</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Leadership & Community Engagement</h2>
          <p>Include examples like:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Student group leadership</li>
            <li>Volunteering</li>
            <li>Mentoring</li>
            <li>Organizing initiatives</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Attach evidence: certificates, photos, letters of support.</p>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Presentation & Communication</h2>
          <p>
            Your application should be clear, concise, and error-free. If
            shortlisted, you must be able to speak confidently in an interview.
          </p>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Selection Process & Scoring</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Academic Performance – 20 pts</li>
            <li>Impact Statement – 20 pts</li>
            <li>Leadership – 20 pts</li>
            <li>Presentation – 10 pts</li>
            <li>Interview – 30 pts</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Application Timeline</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>1 Aug.:</strong> Applications Open</li>
            <li><strong>15 Sep.:</strong> Deadline</li>
            <li><strong>16–30 Sep.:</strong> Review</li>
            <li><strong>1–7 Oct.:</strong> Shortlisting</li>
            <li><strong>10–15 Oct.:</strong> Interviews</li>
            <li><strong>20 Oct.:</strong> Final Results</li>
            <li><strong>1 Nov.:</strong> Award Ceremony</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>How to Apply</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>Read the information pack</li>
            <li>
              Visit:
              <a
                href="/scholarship"
                >Click Here</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>Fill out all sections honestly</li>
            <li>Attach impact statement and supporting docs</li>
            <li>Submit by <strong>15th September 2025</strong></li>
          </ol>
        </section>
  
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Final Message – Think Bigger</h2>
          <p>
            Applying for this scholarship builds the mindset to pursue bigger
            goals. This is just your training ground.
          </p>
          <p class="highlight">Best of luck with your applications!</p>
